Titolo: Knights of the Crystallion

Anno: 1990

Descrizione: Knights of the Crystallion is a 1990 video game for the Amiga developed by Bill Williams and published by U.S. Gold. A fantasy-themed adventure game comprising a mix of sub-games with a puzzle element, the game makes extensive use of the Amiga computer's Hold-And-Modify graphics mode.Psygnosis was offered the game before U.S. Gold, but turned it down for being too weird.